{"tid":1161814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍發布投放巨型鑽地彈片段 by Now TV (TVB 6：30新聞 無報)","createTime":"2019-05-19T12:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T12:26:20.000Z","uid":125193,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1633cf039400e58fc2e60ff7c93f424fca3219f9","tid":1161814,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:26:20.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】在波斯灣局勢緊張之際，美軍在網上發放B-2隱形轟炸機投彈的片段。<br />\n<br />\n空軍在Twitter發放高清片段，看到一架B-2隱形轟炸機，投放兩個GBU-57巨型制導鑽地炸彈，並擊中目標。帖文指每個炸彈重三萬磅，準繩度高，專門對付地下設施，但無說明片段何時何地拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n最近美國和伊朗因核問題關係轉趨緊張，<br />\n美軍調派航母和轟炸機前往波斯灣加強部署。美軍發放鑽地炸彈片段，被視為震懾伊朗的舉措。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=348454\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D348454&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=c2e3060d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D348454&h=2a546648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=348454</a>"}]}